tachyon.master.file.meta

Class TtlBucket

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.master.file.meta.TtlBucket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<TtlBucket>

    public final class TtlBucket
extends Object
implements Comparable<TtlBucket>
    A bucket with all files whose ttl value lies in the bucket's time interval. The bucket's time interval starts at a specific time and lasts for Constants.MASTER_TTLCHECKER_INTERVAL_MS. Not thread-safe. Only for use related to TtlBucketList.
